column3: Trades<If(PlayerParameter(4))>woman<Else/>man</If>, eh? You've that look about you. Interested in putting those skills of yours to use undertaking a leve or two?

It's all above board─all handled under the auspices of the Crystal Exarch, worry not. We process and dole out a mountain of leves every day. Register with us and you can peruse the open ones at your leisure.
You'll be compensated too, in case you were afraid we were running some sort of charity. So─shall I put your name down in the ledger?
Right, then! <Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, was it? Let me just finish filling out this remaining bit of paperwork, and then you'll be all set!
You may now undertake Crystarium leves by speaking with Eirikur.
You dabble in trades? Could've fooled me. Are you sure?
In order to undertake this quest, you must be a Disciple of the Hand or the Land of level 70 or above.
